[[File:Xizor-SOTETPB.png|thumb|right|200px|Xizor, the Dark Prince]]
'''Dark Prince''' was a title used in reference to [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]] during his reign as [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]] of the [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]], where he was known as "[[Underlord]]."

